response.overview: Two high school nobodies make the decision to crash the last major celebration before the new millennium on New Year's Eve 1999. The night becomes even crazier than they could have ever dreamed when the clock strikes midnight.
response.tagline: New Years Eve, 1999. The last party before...
response.title: Y2K

release_dates.note: South by Southwest Film & TV Festival

results.name: The chances of getting absolutely humbled by a kid are low, but they're never zero.
